*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Report ZBK_P015
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&Modal Dialog Box
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
REPORT zbk_p015.

START-OF-SELECTION.

CALL SCREEN 0100 STARTING AT 10 10 ENDING AT 50 20.

*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Module STATUS_0100 OUTPUT
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
MODULE status_0100 OUTPUT.
  SET PF-STATUS '0100'.
  SET TITLEBAR '0100'.
ENDMODULE.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&      Module  USER_COMMAND_0100  INPUT
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*       text
*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
MODULE user_command_0100 INPUT.
  CASE sy-ucomm.
    WHEN '&CANCEL'.
      LEAVE TO SCREEN 0.
  ENDCASE.
ENDMODULE.
